name: Jonathan Martin
text: Fast. Very great food & warm. Fresh. Crew is more a friend than workers. Smiles. They can answer any questions you have of their menu.

name: N Pear
text: Not great. Just as bad as microwaveable pizza. Not to mention they charged us .25 each for our cups of water when we didn't want to spend a lot on their soft drinks or bottled water. Who does that? It's just tap water!
